N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4627.12 - Subpoenas

State Regulations

At the request of any party to an appeal, and for good
cause shown, the commission shall issue subpoenas for the attendance of
witnesses and the production of books, records and other
documents. Notes
